short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides folder structure view for code in GitLab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension provides tree view for code in GitLab. In time of writing description, this is the only extension that supports custom-hosted GitLab instances. The must-have plugin for code reviews! Enjoy :) Note: You can see it only on Commits and Merge Requests. It does NOT work like Octotree.
